<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Votre demande de conge a ete approuvee</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <h2 style="color: #198754;">Demande approuvee</h2>

    <p>Bonjour {{ contributor.firstName }},</p>

    <p>Votre demande de conge a ete approuvee par votre manager.</p>

    <table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 20px 0;">
        <tr><th align="left">Type</th><td>{{ vacation.typeLabel }}</td></tr>
        <tr><th align="left">Du</th><td>{{ vacation.startDate|date('d/m/Y') }}</td></tr>
        <tr><th align="left">Au</th><td>{{ vacation.endDate|date('d/m/Y') }}</td></tr>
        <tr><th align="left">Jours ouvres</th><td>{{ vacation.numberOfWorkingDays }}</td></tr>
    </table>

    <p>Bons conges !</p>

    <p>
        <a href="{{ url('vacation_request_show', {'id': vacation.id.value}) }}"
           style="background-color: #198754; color: #ffffff; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;">
            Voir le detail
        </a>
    </p>

    <hr>
    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">HotOnes — notification automatique.</p>
</body>
</html>
